{"tid":1311260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京嗆制裁對台軍售美企 蔡英文：不需要鄰居說三道四","createTime":"2019-07-13T05:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:50:18.000Z","uid":35519,"like":148,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"05ae4c02c01168c9a3f5485b02ed3b2512989a4a","tid":1311260,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0O2Odn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0O2Odn.png&h=c2eb7126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔特派記者楊淳卉／紐約十二日報導〕總統蔡英文出訪友邦於當地時間11日過境紐約，中國外交部以發言人耿爽名義在官網刊登新聞稿宣布，將對參與此次售台武器的美國企業實施制裁。對此，蔡總統於美東時間12日下午受訪表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>我們過去這段時間努力強化台灣國防及守護台灣民主，希望能對區域的和平穩定做出貢獻，這些都是這段期間來我們很努力做的事情，也不需要我們的鄰居這樣說三道四。</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統在美國紐約過境第二天下午前往哥倫比亞大學，與哥倫比亞大學教授Andrew Nathan等學者及相關領域學生閉門對談，會後於下榻飯店接受媒體聯訪。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統抵達哥大前，就有十餘名中國僑民於場外拉起「不准蔡英文破壞中美關係」布條抗議，高喊「打倒蔡英文、蔡英文滾出美國」。此外，蔡總統於當地時間11日抵達紐約後，也有中國僑民於蔡總統下榻飯店前等候抗議，甚至與在場支持蔡總統的民眾發生肢體衝突。<br />\n<br />\n對於稍早於<strong><ins>中國僑民於哥大前的抗議</ins></strong>，蔡總統表示，他們事先有一定程度的了解，<strong><ins>「這些抗議的人，希望他們也享受一下民主社會的氛圍，但像昨天那樣打人就不好了。」</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"bd8d927f59f69ade40626fa701a4401c6041704b","tid":1311260,"uid":272922,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"蔡英文真係要加油<br />\n唔想見到台灣變成第二個香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bde03aa75a8eb022771d73e479d7502d1be5357","tid":1311260,"uid":267730,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"不需要鄰居說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9e0931f37eb81279b476bb2275f24f8bc1fc9c","tid":1311260,"uid":106634,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:58:06.000Z","msg":"蔡總統一定要守住嚴打間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2daff4ff24c0961f20b5f29f7b5a4cf6cd83602","tid":1311260,"uid":83853,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"台灣國買武器係台灣內部事務，其他國家不得說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6834d1b51adc8021dd99c61105ff5d70d125a9c8","tid":1311260,"uid":35430,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"高喊「打倒蔡英文、蔡英文滾出美國」<br />\n我有冇睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滾出美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你地係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572099804f4c7f522da1ca2074980e4d0b5cba0a","tid":1311260,"uid":1241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"企撚開啲啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d400b9924f4381f5420fc5279dfe763bdab96f6","tid":1311260,"uid":42820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"佢真係執豆咁執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f05f09319c79732dfdaa189148496f2206ab47","tid":1311260,"uid":279311,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責干涉別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0a0278dabbc85a01f549ce33574a0a6981855e","tid":1311260,"uid":54303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3bde03aa75a8eb022771d73e479d7502d1be5357","tid":1311260,"uid":267730,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"不需要鄰居說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"鄰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57492b1c69dcfdc76c95b113f6d4b1b09d23cefd","tid":1311260,"uid":267730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fb0a0278dabbc85a01f549ce33574a0a6981855e","tid":1311260,"uid":54303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid"